Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor Koike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, but she passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Detective Someda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry for your loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are trying to figure \Nout what truly happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you were at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's rough on you\Nbeing so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for her sake,\Nyou have to keep looking forward, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time can heal many wounds in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.89,0:01:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though it won't heal everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.13,0:01:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do even one thing for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was I able...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to repay her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't repay her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think she would be gone so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wanted to repay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't repay her anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 7\NThe End of the Exodus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was there... anything left?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka house - Secret Pizza Sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otosaka, if you haven't eaten yet,\Nwould you like to eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, see, I made some cream stew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yusarin's special cream stew, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:04:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, he's already gone back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something always worth eating!\NYusarin's special cream stew is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a turn-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make Yusa make as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So use your power to break this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can break fortified glass,\Nbut this door is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Due to security reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's made a lot sturdier than normal condos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're so useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I burn this, nothing comes of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My usual sense doesn't shine through at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought I knew the pain of losing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a sister more than the average person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... what happened in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we need a bit more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Then, let's come back again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'm going to just barge in\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's me, Shirayanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was he all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I think he's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm leaving you with the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Shirayanagi,\Nthe one you saved the life of in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you haven't \Nbeen to school ever since...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About your little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in no position to be able to say this,\Nbut is there anything I can do—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything is fine. Otosaka,\NI want to be of help to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help to me?\NThere's no need for that. I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've only been \Neating cup-o-noodles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like them, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... those pancakes we ate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go eat that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pancakes? When did we eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day you saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cup-o-noodles and pancakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aren't they about the same nutrition-wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in any case, we should head outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can I ask you to go\Nbuy cases of cup-o-noodles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to run an errand for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cup-o-noodles. I don't care what kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... Otosaka, you're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to go. I'll pay you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go unless you're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't go unless I'm coming with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirayanagi, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... my legal guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean it like that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in my own way, I think about you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- You're not here to run errands for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Otosaka,\Nit's important for you to step outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay cooped up,\Nyour get more and more ill mentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mentally ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.72,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've been telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People who are fine don't live like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's proof that you are mentally ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go off and treat \Npeople like they're sick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't run errands,\Ncan you go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...\NI'm sorry for doing something unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go stock up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess they're here to \Ncapture me by force...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shirayanagi may have been acting\Nbecause she was asked to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means, this may be \Nthe timing for my exit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this much, I'm sure I can live\Nfor a while without going back home...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Withdrawal\NFee\NBalance Left
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that the soaking wet guy can't find me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to escape to somewhere far away...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I've come pretty far now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Internet and Comic Cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten sick of noodles,\Nso I guess I'll have some pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surprisingly enough, I can be hard to find...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your pizza... and a salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Salad? A free item, huh. I don't want it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So damn boring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How many days has it been?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing has gone on for this long.\NI'm sure they won't find me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go out for just a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fried Mitarashi Dango
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's been a while since\NI last ate something sweet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know there was such a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die! I'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think you're playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This guy hit me with trash,\Ntelling me to get outta the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a normal law-abiding citizen, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A normal law-abiding citizen\Nhits people with trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,\Nif they get pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pull him outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that picked\Na fight with us, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you have to see a bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you win against me? Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure you can't \Nplay games for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that I punched this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, you guys are falling out already?\NYou guys okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... What the hell is going on—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's merely the fact that I'm strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you go against me,\NI'll literally kill you. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You the bastard that knocked\Nout all of Gondo's guys by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gondo? Maybe a guy by that\Nname was in that bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hosoyamada. Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a name that I'm probably\Ngoing to forget in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got some nerve.\NYou think so little of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, teach him a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you bastards doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I crush one eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can get a self-conscious nickname like\N"One-Eyed Hososomething" you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you undecided?\N"One-Eyed" sounds cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,THE Hosoyamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can win against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Real life is more fun than a game!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Is it something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... you... when did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you proceed any further, you won't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to return to being a human ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I stopped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have submitted a leave of \Nabsence request to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel responsible for this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The decision I made back then\Nwas not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have immediately \Nquarantined Ayumi to a safe location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I decided that \NI'll stick it out with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until you have risen back up to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You took my valuable prey—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be crippled for life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to stop being human?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then... what are you saying I should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For starters,\Nhow about you have a decent meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A good meal may be the foundation for energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say a diet of just pizza
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sweet soy sauce mochi skewers is decent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it will calm you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying I should eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me. I'll get it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me. Right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you setting it all up\Nwithout my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just one bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I swear that we
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will not have anything\Nto do with each other ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One bite? Really just one bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That promise is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takajo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takajo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His family home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is here, so rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch some TV or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to make me eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a surprise for you \Nto see when it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Here, it's done.\N- Here, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same taste...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother left behind \Na notebook of recipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I took the liberty of borrowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The page with the omelet rice was the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only one with a big flowery circle on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.44,On Top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Sauce - Have a good day Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely,\Nit was your favorite food in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi, after your mother\Nwas no longer around, saw that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and was probably recreating\Nthat taste for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.41,0:21:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that was... the last omelet rice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...\Nit's sweet, and tastes horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not healthy for you\Nto scarf down food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.18,0:21:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And take this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do from here on..?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about you return\Nto the student council once again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We promised we would never have \Nanything to do with each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After I ate this...\Nyou said that's what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't eat just one bite. You ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I watched, thinking, "Wow, you really \Nwant to have something to do with me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll go back to the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
